25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD53wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=55297489\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD53wIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=ab77bbfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"},{"pid":"6da19e7692605dabcb9284f9af37d46e5dd58d18","tid":1679581,"uid":37739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:55:17.000Z","msg":"振美好嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf88915f75835caa4bcbbc305297c8931587864d","tid":1679581,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:55:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad2993fce7618ffcef8a5ea33395d429b72b9969","tid":1679581,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:55:47.000Z","msg":"細爽幾點食野"},{"pid":"e609861a04e95ca13ba547d691c89f4b75910ad0","tid":1679581,"uid":77104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"聽日都唔好去拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d1c5af705bef4f2b90b1a69c13a36651984657","tid":1679581,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T09